<p>As far as adding external libraries goes, though, do you know which library I’d need to add? I’ve used the method you describe before in plenty of personal projects (for most small projects, I’ll just download the .jar files directly from Maven/wherever they’re hosted), but in this case, I’m not sure which libraries VSCode is expecting to find (and not finding).</p>
